    #home-section3
      .container.text-center
        h2.section-title.text-center Connecting you to the right job
        h5.text-center.description Discover jobs in Malaysia with 3 simple steps
        .row
          .col-xs-12.col-md-4
            .block
              .icon.first
              h4.title(translate='') 1. Create your candidate account
              p.content.text-justify(translate='')
                | Create your Candidate account to get matched to the best opportunities for you. Keep your education and experience as up to-date as possible.
          .col-xs-12.col-md-4
            .block
              .icon.second
              h4.title(translate='') 2. Get matched to jobs
              p.content.text-justify(translate='')
                | Based on your profile and info given, SkootJobs will match you to the best jobs for you. Then you can start messaging and applying for these jobs immediately.
          .col-xs-12.col-md-4
            .block
              .icon.third
              h4.title(translate='') 3. Apply quickly and easily
              p.content.text-justify(translate='')
                | When you see jobs you like, apply quickly and easily. Once you’ve applied, SkootJobs saves your contact details and resume, making future applications easy.
